This app provides you : 

1. Live most accurate Air Quality level in your area through the map

2. Live Weather Report in which Rain chances, Temperature, Rain precipitation, Wind speed, Humidity and Wind Direction are included.

3. Predict weather report upto 7 days.

4. Live concentration level of NO2, CO, SO2, PM2.5, PM10 and O3 which are parameters of Air Pollution level

5. Effect of Air quality level on your health

6. Satellite image of cloud of your area

7. Lightning Alert through map
